# Production Hardening and Cost Transparency in Hive

## Overview

As Hive workflows move toward production environments, reliability and cost visibility become essential for safe and scalable deployment.

This document proposes enhancements to improve workflow resilience, failure recovery, and execution cost awareness.

## Production Hardening

### Retry Policies

Allow workflows or nodes to define retry behavior.

Example:

```yaml
retry:
  max_attempts: 3
  strategy: exponential_backoff


